title: 5 Things You Didn't Know about St. Patrick
text: 5 Things You Didn't Know about St. Patrick 2017 13 Mar Tweet Posted by Kyle Fletcher St. Patrick’s Day is fast approaching, so you had best find something green to wear and quick! As you’re searching though, have you ever asked yourself who Saint Patrick actually was? We all recognize his Irish shamrock, and know that one story about the snakes, but who was he really? The answer to this question may surprise you. Here are 5 things you probably didn’t know about Saint Patrick!
